<ul>
<li>A single-page tool with a clean purple gradient design</li>
<li>Big text area where you can paste any received message</li>
<li>"Get Reply" button that detects what kind of message it is (question, thanks, apology, scheduling, invitation, good news, bad news, etc.)</li>
<li>Three suggested replies: <strong>Friendly</strong> (warm, casual), <strong>Polite</strong> (formal, professional), and <strong>Short</strong> (quick and direct) ŌĆö each color-coded with a copy button</li>
<li>Mobile-friendly responsive layout</li>
<li>Built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript ŌĆö no backend, no frameworks</li>
</ul>
<p>You can paste a message and try it out in the preview. Hit Ōīś/Ctrl + Enter as a shortcut for "Get Reply".</p>
<p><strong>Next, I can add tone customization sliders (e.g., formal/casual, warm/neutral, brief/detailed) so you can fine-tune the reply style. Would you like me to do that?</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view EventContainer-module__w_fMqa__eventContainer"><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view" data-event-id="3bd9bce3-4722-4b69-81d1-9560762e7429" data-commit-id="1619b3a57ab422786b5745e38872b70727fe3742" style="--useView--gap: 2px;"><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view"><button class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view useView-module__vOh_Ha__isHorizontal ExpandableFeedContent-module__mkQqzq__expandableButton Interactive2-module__BR3hWq__shades Interactive2-module__BR3hWq__root Interactive2-module__BR3hWq__transition Interactive2-module__BR3hWq__disabled _sdz_text _sdz_surface-bg _sdz_custom-hover:shades-up-2 _sdz_custom-pressed:shades-up-3 Interactive2-module__BR3hWq__borderRadius Interactive2-module__BR3hWq__focus" style="--useView--gap: 6px; --useView--justify: space-between; --useView--align: center; --useView--pr: 4px; --useView--pl: 4px; --Interactive2--border-radius: 12px;"><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view useView-module__vOh_Ha__isHorizontal" style="--useView--gap: 8px; --useView--align: center; --useView--grow: 1; --useView--shrink: 1;"><div class=" useView-module__vOh_Ha__view _sdz_surface-bg _sdz_surface _sdz_surface-border _sdz_surface-border-strength-subtle ToolUsePrimitives-module__A3-RwW__iconSurface" style="--useView--justify: center; --useView--align: center; --useView--pt: 4px; --useView--pr: 4px; --useView--pb: 4px; --useView--pl: 4px; --useView--border-radius: var(--border-radius-8);"><svg preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMin" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--accent-positive-default)" class="Icon-module__CwnszW__icon " aria-hidden="true" style="--Icon--size: 16px; --Icon--rotate: 0deg; width: 16px; height: 16px;"><path d="M14.47 9.47a.75.75 0 1 1 1.06 1.06l-4 4a.75.7